```plantuml
@startuml opstree_OT-Microservices-Training

actor User
participant Frontend as "Frontend (ReactJS)"
participant Gateway as "Gateway (Spring Boot)"
participant EmployeeService as "Employee Service (Golang)"
participant AttendanceService as "Attendance Service (Golang)"
participant SalaryService as "Salary Service (Golang)"
participant NotificationService as "Notification Service (Python)"
database MySQL as "MySQL"
database Elasticsearch as "Elasticsearch"

User -> Frontend: Accesses employee management UI
Frontend -> Gateway: GET /api/employees
Gateway -> EmployeeService: GET /employees
EmployeeService -> MySQL: Query employee data
MySQL --> EmployeeService: Employee records
EmployeeService --> Gateway: Employee data
Gateway --> Frontend: Employee list

Frontend -> Gateway: POST /api/attendance
Gateway -> AttendanceService: POST /attendance
AttendanceService -> MySQL: Store attendance record
MySQL --> AttendanceService: Success
AttendanceService --> Gateway: Confirmation
Gateway --> Frontend: Success message

Frontend -> Gateway: GET /api/salary/{empId}
Gateway -> SalaryService: GET /salary/{empId}
SalaryService -> Elasticsearch: Query salary data
Elasticsearch --> SalaryService: Salary record
SalaryService --> Gateway: Salary data
Gateway --> Frontend: Salary details

SalaryService -> NotificationService: Trigger notification
NotificationService -> Elasticsearch: Get employee email
Elasticsearch --> NotificationService: Employee email
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Generate email
NotificationService -> NotificationService: Send salary slip email

@enduml
```